Pre-Game Insights: Spencer Arrighetti and Taijuan Walker are the projected starters for the game.
Spencer Arrighetti has been performing well in August with a 2.55 ERA in four starts.
Taijuan Walker has struggled in August with a 9.26 ERA in three starts.
The Astros are one of the top offenses in MLB and are expected to perform well against Walker.
The Phillies have taken the seventh most walks this season, which could be advantageous against Arrighetti's 10.4 percent walk rate.
Philadelphia is playing well at home, being almost 20 games over .500 at Citizens Bank Ballpark.
